import React, { Fragment } from "react";
import { Container } from "react-bootstrap";
import { Dropdown } from "react-bootstrap";
import { ButtonGroup } from "react-bootstrap";

export default function Search() {
    return (
        <Fragment>
            <Container id="ContainerMainPage">
                <ButtonGroup>
                    <Dropdown>
                        <Dropdown.Toggle id="genre" variant="outline-light">
                            Género
                        </Dropdown.Toggle>
                        <Dropdown.Menu variant="light">
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1" active>
                                Acción
                            </Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Drama</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Comedia</Dropdown.Item>
                        </Dropdown.Menu>
                    </Dropdown>
                    <Dropdown id="btnSort">
                        <Dropdown.Toggle id="sort" variant="outline-light">
                            Ordenar por
                        </Dropdown.Toggle>
                        <Dropdown.Menu variant="light">
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1" active>
                                Pelicula
                            </Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Serie</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Comedia</Dropdown.Item>
                        </Dropdown.Menu>
                    </Dropdown>
                </ButtonGroup>
                <hr className="hr"></hr>
            </Container>
        </Fragment>
    );
}
